{"tid":484002,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"好憎做香港人","createTime":"2017-11-29T16:26:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-29T17:29:43.000Z","uid":89840,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ed39c02329382ae969ec36a62f47ebd8c790d854","tid":484002,"uid":89840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T16:26:31.000Z","msg":"到底前世做錯咩先會成為香港人<br />\n唔係有錢人<br />\n自問由細已經好努力讀書<br />\n讀完u出黎捱生捱死<br />\n晚晚ot<br />\n望住自己份糧 再望下個樓價<br />\n我真係唔知幾時先可以買到一層樓<br />\n就算他朝有日畀我儲夠首期<br />\n淨低幾廿年都要為左果幾百呎樓疲於奔命<br />\n我唔想成世做奴隸"},{"pid":"09586e0cef2d4e0bdf2127fe34e11747167ca565","tid":484002,"uid":58195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T16:39:25.000Z","msg":"點先唔叫做奴隸"},{"pid":"4cb6ead3e0afe6528dac8fb00de9908f0a7c1589","tid":484002,"uid":89840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T17:22:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點先唔叫做奴隸</blockquote><br />\n起碼唔洗住豆腐潤咁大既屋<br />\n仲要做供成世樓"},{"pid":"0d9d210f609ac52b67df7822e2994520e383206a","tid":484002,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T17:29:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}